- Don't dawdle.

651
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:16,680
Keep up.

652
00:32:18,510 --> 00:32:19,350
Hurry up and follow.

653
00:32:20,790 --> 00:32:21,680
I'm going anyway.

654
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,280
Miss Song.

655
00:32:28,110 --> 00:32:28,960
Miss Song.

