00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:30,310
Miss Song.

657
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:32,950
Miss Song,

658
00:32:33,310 --> 00:32:34,700
why do this?

659
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:35,720
The journey is long.

660
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,390
It'll take several days on horseback.

661
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,790
