in the ordinary alleys♪

679
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:56,010
♪A thousand unspeakable thoughts♪

680
00:33:56,180 --> 00:34:02,380
♪The withered mandala flowers
bring a dream of the past♪

681
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:08,120
