as Chu Yu,

688
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:30,550
so

689
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:32,760
don't drive me away, okay?

690
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:36,800
♪Yet memories are lingering♪

691
00:34:37,010 --> 00:34:42,140
♪Making me want to return to the past♪

692
